DWFToolkit::DWFRenderable Class Reference
[DWF Package API]

#include "dwf/package/Renderable.h"

List of all members.

Detailed Description

DWFObject and DWFFeature derive from this class to allow polymorphic access to them.

Since:
7.2.0
This class exists solely to allow polymorphic access to DWFObject and DWFFeature, both of which derive from this.
Examples:

ReadContentDefinition/ReadContentDefinition.cpp.
